==生物化学==
空气中微量香堇酮就能被嗅觉捕获。α-香堇酮的阈值为3ppb（3×10−7mg/L），β-香堇酮位0.12ppb、(R)-γ-香堇酮为11ppb、(S)-γ-香堇酮为0.07ppb。<ref>Elisabetta Brenna, Claudio Fuganti, Stefano Serra, and Philip Kraft, Optically Active Ionones and Derivatives: Preparation and Olfactory Properties, [[Eur._J._Org._Chem.|Eur. J. Org. Chem.]], 2002, S. 967–978.</ref>
